content: double_crochet 1 t in skipped st 1 double_crochet in next st** repeat from * to ** to marked stitch 3 double_crochet in next stitch 1 double_crochet in next st repeat from * to ** to last st 2 double_crochet in last st turn row 62 repeat row 3 fasten_off weave in ends block and keep your eyes open for fairies rev 6/16/2024 darnknitanyway com ©2024 darn knit anyway all rights reserved this is a free pattern stillwater mn 651-342-1386 we hope you make beautiful crochet items for yourself or your loved ones
